ockquote><blockquote>大紀元.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw已經太遲，支那高官，有錢人，一早已經申請左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你覺得特朗普唔會清算呢班人? 一句話扣起晒佢地D錢再丟佢地返大陸都得啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以仿效加拿大，如果條友長期唔係加國而又無報或交稅，政府可取消該國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04444826703139c9aee036a87d985bad3cac8865","tid":123152,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:47:35.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da43f30f97ed938f514d5711fc48efb7e7ccd66","tid":123152,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T04:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54055fdc7070cc6637149a765cf807de9b70e857","tid":123152,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}